
DATA DESCRIPTION:
Screenplay scraped from IMSDb in  July 2025 using rvest. Saved as raw .txt in InputData folder.

DATA CLEANING:
Used 02_tokenise_analysis.R to split into dialogue and speaker lines. Removed stop words using tidytext and saved intermediate files to AnalysisData.

ANALYSIS:
- Identified top 5 TF-IDF terms per speaker
- Plotted frequency of “sith lord” bigram throughout script

OUTPUT FILES:
- Heatmap of TF-IDF: tfidf_heatmap.png
- Bigram timeline chart: top_clean_bigrams.png

